description:
Danny recaps this week's Vanderpump Rules. The gang finishes up their Mexico trip and heads back to SUR, where Brittany finalizes her guest list for her engagement party, and Raquel/James finalize their guest list for their puppy party. Danny also briefly looks back on KLG & Hoda's final episode.
